Our Electrical Services
We handle a wide range of electrical work for both residential and commercial clients. Here is what we offer:

New Electrical Installations and Wiring
Building a new home, adding a room, or fitting out a commercial space? We handle full electrical installations from scratch, including all wiring, plug points, light circuits and distribution board setup. Every new installation is designed properly and completed to SANS standards.

DB Board Upgrades and Repairs
An old or overloaded distribution board is one of the most common causes of electrical problems in South African homes and businesses. If your board keeps tripping, you are running too many appliances on too few circuits, or your board is simply outdated, we can assess it and upgrade it to handle your current load safely.

Fault Finding and Emergency Callouts
If something has stopped working and you do not know why, we will find the fault and fix it. We offer fault finding and emergency electrical services across the Helderberg and Boland. Same-day support is available when possible, and we respond quickly because we know that electrical faults rarely happen at a convenient time.

Certificate of Compliance (COC)
A COC is a legal requirement when selling or renting a property in South Africa. It confirms that the electrical installation has been inspected and meets the required safety standards. Our registered electricians carry out the inspection, identify anything that needs attention, carry out the necessary repairs, and issue the certificate. We make the process as straightforward as possible.

Generator Installation and Changeover
Load shedding is not going away, and a standby generator gives you reliable backup power when the grid goes down. We install generators and the changeover systems that switch your supply safely between the grid and the generator. This is especially important for businesses, hospitals, retirement centres and other properties where power cuts have a serious impact.

